00:03:52,000 --> 00:04:02,000
Clearly that is continuous, but it is not differentiable at <i>x</i> = 0. There’s a corner at <i>x</i> = 0.
显然函数连续 但<i>x</i>=0处是不可微 <i>x</i>=0处存在拐角

