观察区间变为不那么对称的[-0.5，1] 这是这个区间

43
00:05:00,000 --> 00:05:11,000
Now we notice that the secant line at <i>x</i> = −0.5 and <i>x</i> = 1, the line joining those two points,
注意到 连接<i>x</i> = −0.5和<i>x</i> = 1两点的割线

